rows.label: qst002206_msg0001
rows.name: So, um...how did your investigation go?

rows.label: qst002206_msg0002
rows.name:
So there was an Invidian girl in the
refugee camp who was trying to get
into the Choir just like me?

rows.label: qst002206_msg0004
rows.name: I can't say I recognize the name.

rows.label: qst002206_msg0007
rows.name:
There was only one open spot at the
last audition. I guess because I passed,
she must have...

rows.label: qst002206_msg0008
rows.name:
Um, could you come with me for a bit?
I'd like to meet this Albina and talk to
her in person.

rows.label: qst002206_msg0009
rows.name:
I-it'll be all right! I can handle it!
As long as you're with me, I mean...

rows.label: qst002206_msg0010
rows.name:
I want to talk this over properly!
Come on, let's go!
